headline.print_headline: Asia Stages Improbable EurAsia Cup Comeback
headline.main: Asia Stages Improbable EurAsia Cup Comeback

lead_paragraph: Asia staged an improbable Ryder Cup-like comeback on the final day of the EurAsia Cup on Saturday, picking up seven of 10 points available in singles to level the score at 10-all and share the trophy with Europe.
